headline: Should You Buy Airbnb Stock Before May 13?
summary: Airbnb has been teasing an expansion in the business for several quarters now.  Airbnb's growth has slowed, meaning the company could use a catalyst to accelerate its growth.  For years, Airbnb (NASDAQ: ABNB) has been teasing the idea of expanding the business "beyond the core."

headline: Airbnb brings AI customer service agent to half of US customers
summary: “It's already led to a 15% reduction in people needing to contact live human agents," CEO Brian Chesky said.
